data.author: Killerpokemon

changelog.release_notes: This is a Watchface Made for the Pebble Time. I just got my new Pebble time Red in the mail today, so I decided to make a watchface for it, I used a new website to make the watchface, so I couldn't figure out how to add the date to the watchface. But it shows the Time, and the Skrillex Logo.
